  "core_payload": {
    "content_type": "markdown",
    "content": "# Roadmap\n\n## 1. Role\nRoadmap will become a more adaptive strategic timeline that can hold alternative futures, branch posture, capacity notes, and review anchors without collapsing into vague ambition.\n\n## 2. Future Roadmap Contract\nRoadmap will support stronger phase models across major horizons, clearer separation between exploratory, committed, and promotion-ready phases, richer review anchors tied to evidence and execution pressure, and better compression into daily action through Planning Horizon Engine.\n\n## 3. Operational Consequence\nLong-horizon structure will stay intelligible while adapting under pressure. Roadmap will remain a living planning instrument that guides execution without becoming brittle, decorative, or disconnected from tracker evidence.\n\n## 4. Philosophical Alignment\nRoadmap supports To Dig Deep by making long-horizon intent explicit, reviewable, and compressible into reality."
  },
